sp.p:
His grace presents you by me a chaine, as his gratefull remembrance
for—I am ignorant for what, marry yee may impart:
Yet howsoeuer—come—deare friend:

I am as common in the Court as an hostesses lippes in the countrey;
knights, and clownes, and knaues, and all share mee: the
Court cannot possibly be without me. Adue Maleuole.

